      "time_str": "00:37.150",
      "text": "爱你我愿意去等候",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.72,
      "time_str": "00:40.720",
      "text": "那怕再过几年秋",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.56,
      "time_str": "00:44.560",
      "text": "为爱情孤军奋斗 抛开世俗的信守",
